data.description:
One bdrm/one bath apartment/in law suite available in a desirable neighborhood near Navy Golf Course. Furnished for the most part, no tv or linens or kitchen pots/pans/plates/utensils etc. There is a complete full size galley kitchen with bar separating it from living room. The kitchen also has a dishwasher/gas stove with oven, full fridge, microwave, and updated double ceramic sink. The bedroom is a decent size with a full closet with mirrored doors, it is fully furnished with newer queen sized bed and matching coastal armoire, dresser, and two night tables. There is a ceiling fan in both bedroom and living room. The bathroom comes complete with shower/tub combo, water saving toilet and pedestal sink/mirror. The new full sized washer and dryer are in the bathroom. You have your own private entrance and your own thermostat. There is a fire pit to enjoy in back yard. Move in date negotiable. Should be available for move in by Sunday, Oct. 4th. One month deposit and first months rent due prior to move in. Looking for clean, quiet, drug free person(s) intending to stay awhile. No short term leases available. Must have references of prior rental history. do not email

all utilities included plus wifi. smoking only outside and no flicked butts in the yard. I will only consider a cat, no dogs. There is off street parking for up to two vehicles.
